name: Velouria (Fire Emblem Fates)
description:
Velouria from Fire Emblem Fates


This was my first LoRA, and i didnt knew half of what i know now, so i decided to remake it

Use velouria_fates as trigger word.

Trained on Nai

You may want to add "red eyes, gray hair, multicolored hair, animal ears, red hood, pants" to your Prompt


Can be used at 1.0 weight but you should lower to 0.7 or 0.8 it if you want to change her clothes and maybe you will need to add "belt, buckle, corset" to your negative prompt as well

All images were generated using yabalMix (https://civitai.com/models/28648/yabalmix) with xformers on and using kl-f8-anime2 vae.

images were generated at 512x768 and upscaled using highres fix by 1.95 and using 4x_foolhardy_Remacri upscaler
